***** '''Player:''' No deal.
***** '''Mage of Zamorak:''' Fine. I will find another way.
***** {{tact|end}}
**** {{topt|I need to think about it.}}
***** '''Player:''' I need to think about it.
***** '''Mage of Zamorak:''' I will be here once you have decided.
***** {{tact|end}}
